http://www.codejava.net/servers/tomcat/how-to-deploy-a-java-web-application-on-tomcat



Find out how to enable debugging port on tomcat in ubuntu



set JPDA_ADDRESS=8000
set JPDA_TRANSPORT=dt_socket
to start server in debug mode:

%TOMCAT_HOME%/bin/catalina.bat jpda start
For unix first export variables:

export JPDA_ADDRESS=8000
export JPDA_TRANSPORT=dt_socket
and to start server in debug mode:

%TOMCAT_HOME%/bin/catalina.sh jpda start